{"tid":1673999,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"殺房東再棄屍 港男維持原判囚15年 2016年05月17日(二) 11:55","createTime":"2019-10-25T03:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T07:23:28.000Z","uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce19e981923f584a6f7343aff8086c202e32f41","tid":1673999,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"殺房東再棄屍 港男維持原判囚15年<br />\n2016年05月17日(二) 11:55<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160517/photo/bkn-20160517115511124-0517_00822_001_01b.jpg?20160517123308\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160517%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160517115511124-0517_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20160517123308&h=5a6d6e9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麥家祺不滿遭催繳房租，誘殺房東後棄屍，判囚15年。(資料圖片)<br />\n1/2<br />\n被台北文化大學退學的香港僑生麥家祺不滿遭催繳房租，誘殺房東後棄屍，一度被判無期徒刑；台灣高等法院及後考慮麥與被害人家屬和解，並賠償近500萬台幣，依殺人罪改判有期徒刑15年，最高法院今天再駁回控方上訴，維持原判，麥被判囚15年。<br />\n<br />\n24歲的麥家祺2009年申請到台灣就讀文化大學，以每學年10萬台幣向林姓房東承租套房，2014年9月他因沒按時交租被房東催討，麥家祺佯稱冷氣需要修理，誘使房東上門檢查，雙方之後爆發口角，麥家祺持啞鈴襲擊房東並持刀殺死對方，隨後以棉被包裹屍體棄屍。<br />\n<br />\n麥在一審時坦承犯案，並當庭道歉，又稱曾打電話報案，符合自首減刑條件，惟法官審理後認為他不符合減刑條件，考慮他認罪，依殺人罪判處無期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n二審則認為，麥是因不滿被催租而剝奪他人生命，但考慮他和家屬達成和解，而同意賠償的500萬台幣，只剩18萬台幣未支付，改判他15年有期徒刑。而最高法院審理後，今天駁回控方上訴。"},{"pid":"5cd6af8745cbedbfaf6d68202c44a01090a88ea2","tid":1673999,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T04:25:03.000Z","msg":"貼夠舊新聞未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c801e40514685f969ea46d303e1be15995b744","tid":1673999,"uid":327909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T04:26:11.000Z","msg":"CLS"},{"pid":"36543eae09c146ba757c63deec02c12528915c4e","tid":1673999,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cd6af8745cbedbfaf6d68202c44a01090a88ea2","tid":1673999,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T04:25:03.000Z","msg":"貼夠舊新聞未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T04:38:43.000Z","msg":"但係有參考價值先會回帶"},{"pid":"cebd8a85f5bcf9ad5b97cdafb0f894cc3c8c3e09","tid":1673999,"uid":3311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T04:41:04.000Z","msg":"賠到500萬都唔肯交1學年10 萬租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4345aeed4644bd986513e2e6c54bce4d4e6760e6","tid":1673999,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T04:41:14.000Z","msg":"殺人應該最少30年<br />\n15年太少"},{"pid":"8a4af807c4c3e521620c76e07c97b57521406296","tid":1673999,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T04:48:59.000Z","msg":"台灣殺人判好輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6922397cde955d0c4c66d7de9fc9ce560233460a","tid":1673999,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cebd8a85f5bcf9ad5b97cdafb0f894cc3c8c3e09","tid":1673999,"uid":3311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T04:41:04.000Z","msg":"賠到500萬都唔肯交1學年10 萬租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T04:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eda45d2725a7bd78c1615ef0a56d5390c7b4a30","tid":1673999,"uid":53187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:13:45.000Z","msg":"算唔算比錢了事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c20404414d8a9897f7a51179147f5031ac2dbb8","tid":1673999,"uid":158806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"台灣高等法院及後考慮麥與被害人家屬和解，並賠償近500萬台幣，依殺人罪改判有期徒刑15年<br />\n<br />\n可以賠錢免死/換減刑，同中東的國家差唔多"}]}